        "timestamp": 1781101918
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I'd do like <code>Bigbig :: { digits : List(U64) }.{ ... }</code></p>",
        "id": 601812189,
        "sender_full_name": "Richard Feldman",
        "timestamp": 1781101973
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>and <code>from_numeral</code> should return <code>Try(Bigbig, ...)</code></p>",
        "id": 601812579,
        "sender_full_name": "Richard Feldman",
        "timestamp": 1781102045
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Is Try.Ok() not a Try ?</p>",
        "id": 601812838,
        "sender_full_name": "TheoTheTorch",
        "timestamp": 1781102092
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Oh, you mean the Bigbig should not be inside a union.</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">Bigbig</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">digits</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">List</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">U64</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">}.{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">plus</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">|</span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">_b</span><span class=\"o\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">#</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">TODO</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">minus</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">|</span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">_b</span><span class=\"o\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">#</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">TODO</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">from_numeral</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Numeral</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Try</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">Bigbig</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"n\">InvalidNumeral</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">..</span><span class=\"p\">])</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">from_numeral</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">|</span><span class=\"n\">literal</span><span class=\"o\">|</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"k\">match</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">U64</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">from_numeral</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">literal</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"nb\">Err</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">_</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">                </span><span class=\"n\">Try</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"nb\">Err</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">InvalidNumeral</span><span class=\"p\">())</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"nb\">Ok</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">value</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">                </span><span class=\"n\">Try</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"nb\">Ok</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"n\">digits</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">List</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">value</span><span class=\"p\">)}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>I feel I've gotten closer with this x)</p>",
        "id": 601814503,
        "sender_full_name": "TheoTheTorch",
        "timestamp": 1781102411
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Oh, List literals are made like [1, 2, 3, 4], not List(1, 2, 3, 4).</p>",
        "id": 601816746,
        "sender_full_name": "TheoTheTorch",
        "timestamp": 1781102783
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>This now compiles:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">from_numeral</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">|</span><span class=\"n\">literal</span><span class=\"o\">|</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"k\">match</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">U64</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">from_numeral</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">literal</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"nb\">Err</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">_</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">                </span><span class=\"n\">Try</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"nb\">Err</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">InvalidNumeral</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s\">\"ohno\"</span><span class=\"p\">))</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"nb\">Ok</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">value</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">                </span><span class=\"n\">Try</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"nb\">Ok</span><span class=\"p\">({</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">digits</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"n\">value</span><span class=\"p\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">})</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>But trying to actually use this has an interesting effect:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code>_lol : Bigbig\n_lol = 1\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Segfault caught: EXCEPTION_ACCESS_VIOLATION (segfault) (code 0xC0000005)<br>\nDev backend execution error: error.DevEvaluatorFailed</p>",
